{"tid":1705391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"早早肯咁做，今日就唔會有人中槍，你地連思想武裝都懶撚過閪，革乜撚野命？","createTime":"2019-11-11T01:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T01:56:49.000Z","uid":170142,"like":43,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5c79e9bb0f8d70f3a612a637311c0be48fc3cf3a","tid":1705391,"uid":170142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:18:04.000Z","msg":"《導正歪風》不要說&ldquo;唔搶槍&rdquo;，試說&ldquo;根本唔應該帶槍&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1586872\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1586872</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n喺9月尾有班垃圾喺到嗌搶槍就割，話我地唔會搶槍，一班思維永遠只會長他人志氣滅自己威風嘅撚樣，搶槍有咩好割？你地明唔明個思維係要話俾班狗聽，你帶得槍出嚟，就預咗會俾我搶，唔想死你就唔好帶槍出嚟<br />\n<br />\n當事件事仲未升溫到宜家咁已經講過，全世界無一個先進國家係會允許警察喺處理大型群眾活動時帶槍，嗰陣仲可以靠禁制令去限制對方行動，而且係有理有據，唔聽就自己承受返個惡果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096ef157f1a0fa041a626ed67bba9cc1e40bb0a8","tid":1705391,"uid":170142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:19:05.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"cb5e6ea0cb30a07df7d7e10b5328e1a64e15944e","tid":1705391,"uid":170142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:19:24.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"35924a5b6816276978e1acad290aea54c10fdd6c","tid":1705391,"uid":170142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:19:49.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"4e59192e1e7a956c1428b7c7af2859fde7f15eeb","tid":1705391,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:20:15.000Z","msg":"我用最卑微嘅心，求吓你哋<br />\n<br />\n香港人，忍無可忍！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1705050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1705050</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"18149ab5d516cd02dbd2a260a02e977ae862fb65","tid":1705391,"uid":170142,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:20:33.000Z","msg":"限制警狗帶槍唔推成主流言論，班狗開槍又有咩壓力可言？"},{"pid":"46c817419a2d01a88b122c4be59ec896dd69c410","tid":1705391,"uid":170142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re